  <brief_title>RSV-MVA-BN Vaccine Phase II Trial in ≥ 55 Year Old Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Single-blind, Placebo Controlled, Dose-ranging Phase II Trial in ≥ 55 Year Old Adults to Evaluate the Safety and Immunogenicity of the Recombinant MVA-BN-RSV Vaccine</official_title>
  <sponsors>
